      <div class="vn-feat-card vn-reveal vn-delay-1"><span class="vn-feat-num">02</span><svg class="vn-feat-icon" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none"><rect x="4" y="4" width="24" height="24" stroke="#0f0f0f" stroke-width="1"/><rect x="10" y="10" width="12" height="12" stroke="#0f0f0f" stroke-width="1"/></svg><h3 class="vn-feat-title">Dual LCD Display</h3><p class="vn-feat-desc">Two precision silver LCD panels give you full control over rotation direction, speed, and daily turns per rotor pair.</p></div>
      <div class="vn-feat-card vn-reveal vn-delay-2"><span class="vn-feat-num">03</span><svg class="vn-feat-icon" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none"><path d="M4 28 L16 4 L28 28 Z" stroke="#0f0f0f" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/></svg><h3 class="vn-feat-title">Piano Lacquer Finish</h3><p class="vn-feat-desc">High-gloss piano black lacquer over a rigid shell with carbon fibre side panels — a finish that rivals the watches themselves.</p></div>
      <div class="vn-feat-card vn-reveal"><span class="vn-feat-num">04</span><svg class="vn-feat-icon" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none"><rect x="4" y="14" width="24" height="14" rx="1" stroke="#0f0f0f" stroke-width="1"/><path d="M10 14V10a6 6 0 0112 0v4" stroke="#0f0f0f" stroke-width="1"/></svg><h3 class="vn-feat-title">Security Key Lock</h3><p class="vn-feat-desc">Chrome barrel key lock secures the full-glass door, protecting your collection with precision hardware you can trust.</p></div>
      <div class="vn-feat-card vn-reveal vn-delay-1"><span class="vn-feat-num">05</span><svg class="vn-feat-icon" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none"><path d="M16 3 L18 13 L28 13 L20 19 L23 29 L16 23 L9 29 L12 19 L4 13 L14 13 Z" stroke="#0f0f0f" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/></svg><h3 class="vn-feat-title">Silent Motor Technology</h3><p class="vn-feat-desc">Ultra-quiet Japanese motors ensure near-silent operation at all speeds. Your watches wind while you sleep — you won't hear a thing.</p></div>
      <div class="vn-feat-card vn-reveal vn-delay-2"><span class="vn-feat-num">06</span><svg class="vn-feat-icon" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none"><circle cx="16" cy="16" r="12" stroke="#0f0f0f" stroke-width="1"/><path d="M16 10V16L21 19" stroke="#0f0f0f" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg><h3 class="vn-feat-title">Adjustable Turn Settings</h3><p class="vn-feat-desc">Set 650, 1000, or 1800 turns per day. CW, CCW, or alternating — engineered to match any calibre's specification.</p></div>
