      <div class="vn-ni vn-reveal"><span class="vn-ni-num">04</span><h4 class="vn-ni-title">Programmable TPD</h4><p class="vn-ni-desc">Set turns-per-day from 650 to 1800. Each rotor pair independently programmable for any manufacturer's spec.</p></div>
